      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Bridge + Declaration Golden Path Checklist\n\nThis is the manual QA script we should be able to run from a blank graph.\n\nHow to use:\n- Walk step-by-step from **Step 1** onward.\n- For each step, mark it **PASS** or **FAIL** in the step node.\n- If you hit a FAIL, write a minimal repro note and the observed behavior.\n\nThis flow is the standard gate for primitives: if this is solid, the rest of beta readiness becomes much lower risk."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "bridge-decl-checklist-known-refs",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Known Refs",
      "position": { "x": 80, "y": -760 },
      "width": 520,
      "height": 280,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Known Good Target Refs\n\nUse these for steps that require a target:\n\n- Edge class library: `/library/classes/edges/root.node#root`\n- Node class library (templates): `/library/classes/nodes/root.node#root`\n- A task graph (beta readiness): `/tasks/beta-readiness/root.node#root`\n\nIf a ref fails to resolve, capture diagnostics from the bridge properties panel."
      }
    },

    {
