      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": { "markdown": "## Step 1: Open A Brand New Graph\n\nAction:\n- Open a brand new graph (blank canvas).\n- Ensure you are in **edit** mode.\n\nResult:\n- [ ] PASS\n- [ ] FAIL\n\nNotes:" }
